Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.48,0:00:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A racing second hand,\Na glittering galaxy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.14,0:00:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan's logic is good medicine\Nfor hearts dried by modern society!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.86,0:00:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's case has a crazy\Nsecret behind a kidnapping!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.29,0:00:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sees the single\Ntruth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.71,0:00:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and looks like a kid but\Nhas the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.65,0:00:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.05,0:01:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Genta, Mitsuhiko, Ayumi,\Nand I were playing Kick-the-Can,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.26,0:02:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but soon found ourselves\Nhaving lunch at a restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with Two-Mix vocalist,\NTakayama Minami-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She had snuck out to look for her\Nmissing partner, Nagano Shiina-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But at the restaurant, she was\Nkidnapped before our very eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.07,0:02:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The kidnappers demanded\Nthe bag she left at the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's more, they\Ndemanded that we take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared they were\Nafter a Two-Mix demo tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.09,0:02:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After taking the bag as ordered,\Nthe kidnappers contacted us
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and said to lose the officers and\Nhave Ayumi deliver the tape alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.68,0:02:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't put Ayumi in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I devised a plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.74,0:03:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any cops around, I hope?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there doesn't\Nseem to be anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready to come, like I told ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try my hardest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.47,0:03:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Popular Artists\NAbduction Case (Part 2)."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Conan-{\i1}kun {\i0}and \NAyumi-{\i1}kun {\i0}switched places?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My word...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The kidnappers\Nare after the demo tape!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said to have Ayumi\Ndeliver it and to lose the police--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so Conan-{\i1}kun {\i0}switched with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, why didn't\Nyou tell us you switched?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'd be most off guard if we\Nlet them think their plan worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:04:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Conan-{\i1}kun {\i0}said we couldn't\Nlet anyone know until then!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, now we can't\Nlocate the kidnappers...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0} is in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he said that these\NTracking Glasses should--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, Conan's\Ngonna get all the credit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can still find their\Nhideout and then tell the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, after we've saved Two-Mix...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:29.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Junior Detective\NLeague Saves the Day!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.45,0:04:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok! Let's go catch those kidnappers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you shouting about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we were saying,\N"Oh! We're so hungry!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.81,0:04:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah... We were saying,\N"Oh! We're so hungry!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:05:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're off to buy some food!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back quickly, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.15,0:05:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ We're so hungry!\NWe're so hungry! We're so hungry! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.84,0:05:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As agreed, it looks\Nlike you came alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, bring the tape up to the\N2nd floor of the nearby warehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your beloved Two-Mix is waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.85,0:05:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't be needing you anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say your prayers\Nwhile you still have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought it, Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks, little girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's the guy\Nfrom the coffee shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:05:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he out somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.42,0:06:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No question about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0} is ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.80,0:06:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to contact\Nthe police for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a phone booth over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.94,0:06:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1-1-9...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! That's the fire department!\NThe police is 110!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.42,0:06:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And don't you need\Nto press this button?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is 110.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Inspector Megure, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.42,0:06:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Where'd you go,\Nlittle boy? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.76,0:06:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you find us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was told to bring this tape here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.43,0:07:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they really questioned\Nus about where the tape was...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why would they want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's save the details\Nfor after we've escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the police are on their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.11,0:07:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're on their way here right now,\Nusing my Tracking Glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It homes in on\Nthis badge's transmitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.45,0:07:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Edogawa Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.79,0:07:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.46,0:07:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry before the\Nother kidnapper comes back...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.63,0:07:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are those your\N"Tracking Glasses"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.18,0:07:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught 'em snooping around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiots! Why didn't you\Ngive the glasses to the police?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.03,0:07:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have plenty of time to fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.07,0:07:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in the afterlife!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm nice enough to turn\Nyou into ashes. Be grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.09,0:08:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! At least tell us\Nwhy you kidnapped us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.85,0:08:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask Buddha in the afterlife.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The countdown bell sounds..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.10,0:08:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"and says to change hearts and run."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"It rings once, twice..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.44,0:08:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Like the sound of off-season fireworks..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.95,0:08:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Like the sound of someone,\Nsomewhere, confessing their love..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. The lyrics\Non the Two-Mix demo tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the reason\Nyou kidnapped Two-Mix!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.46,0:08:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right,\NMiyahara Satoshi-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The night of New Year's Eve,\Nyou killed a man near Shoenji Temple
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and were investigated\Nby Inspector Megure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.26,0:09:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,New Year's Eve?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.68,0:09:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoenji?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.14,0:09:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's where we came\Nup with that song!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.73,0:09:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a murder near that\Ntemple when the bell rang at 11:50...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.15,0:09:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the man died holding the gun,\Nhad gunpowder on his hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and there was an empty\Nshell in the barrel,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.00,0:09:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the police believed your claim\Nthat it went off during your struggle
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.59,0:09:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with the gun-toting maniac.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, that wasn't actually the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had brought the gun\Nto kill him from the very start!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After shooting him through\Nthe heart with the first shot,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.73,0:09:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you loaded another bullet into\Nthe barrel and fired at the ground...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with his hand on the gun, to leave\Nbehind traces of gunpowder!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were no witnesses around,\Nso while you called the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the man sleeping outside was to\Nrun off with the extra bullet and shell
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to put you in the clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, there were people\Nwho heard those sounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mean--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You two from Two-Mix.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The "countdown bell"\Nwas the New Year's bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two fireworks\Nwere the two gunshots.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.56,0:10:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the line, "1996 just flew right by,"\Nindicated the year it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Add in Shoenji Temple,\Nwhich you mentioned on the radio,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the time and place of\Nthe gunshots becomes clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I assume you heard the radio show\Nthe demo tape was played on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.21,0:10:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you kidnapped Two-Mix...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.92,0:10:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to get rid of the tape and\Nthem before the police found out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.92,0:11:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.28,0:11:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I'm Miyahara Satoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy I killed was an old\Nbank-robbing partner of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He suddenly threatened\Nto tell the cops, so I offed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you have\Njust run off after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A temple priest had seen my\Nface while I was on my way there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luckily, he was hard of hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.13,0:11:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Said he had to stay at the temple\Nto ring the bell, so I let him live.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never expected someone to hear\Nthe shots and make a song about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.81,0:11:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cell phone, huh? Give it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:12:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is that long-haired guy's\Nphone I had my partner hold onto...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, can't be careless around you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.70,0:12:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, even if you did call the police,\Nyou'd die before they get here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, please enjoy your stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Inspector Megure.\NI let them and those kids go unharmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.35,0:12:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's odd. He didn't even\Nmention Conan-{\i1}kun {\i0}switching places...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector. I just got word on the radio
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that some kids had called\N110 and asked for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.38,0:12:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! When?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.11,0:12:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, some fifteen minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't they tell us sooner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.72,0:12:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't state their emergency,\Nso the operator thought it was a prank.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do we know the location?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.75,0:13:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it was too short to trace...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad! If the kidnappers\Nwere the ones who hung up...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use! It's not budging!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok! Time for my Power Kick Shoes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! It's no use!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.21,0:13:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you kids ok?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.71,0:13:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!\NAt this rate, we won't survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't breathe the smoke!\NGet lower to the--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.47,0:13:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ok?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:13:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about a nuisance...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.78,0:14:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those annoying cops...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Quit--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! We're long gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're calling from a police box!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.91,0:14:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See for yourself\Nif you don't believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.14,0:14:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.85,0:14:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.06,0:14:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did they get out?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.61,0:14:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See! Told you this\NEarring Cell Phone was useful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.99,0:14:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure was!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.82,0:14:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! We can still\Nget to the concert in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone duck!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.76,0:15:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mock me, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.09,0:15:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna kill each one of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was awesome, Minami-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.48,0:15:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten minutes later, a fire truck\Narrived with police cars,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.75,0:15:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the two-man gang\Nwas put under arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, the Junior Detective\NLeague got a harsh scolding,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.34,0:15:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Takayama Minami-{\i1}san\N{\i0}stuck up for us, so we were acquitted
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then we rushed to the\NBudokan in Inspector Megure's car.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.39,0:16:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already thirty minutes past!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.27,0:16:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good. The crowd's getting antsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.07,0:16:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to go change,\Nso wait backstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.28,0:16:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Backstage?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We wanna introduce\Nyou to everyone later!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.04,0:16:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.54,0:16:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Is Minami-{\i1}chan {\i0}still not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.34,0:16:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez! What's she doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.09,0:16:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Is this backstage?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now!\NYou're not allowed back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.93,0:16:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back to your seats!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takayama-{\i1}san {\i0}told us to come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Minami-{\i1}chan{\i0}'s here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok! Put the opening song on standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.73,0:16:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Someone go to the dressing\Nrooms and ask how much longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, what does this do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't touch that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.91,0:17:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.54,0:17:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! The song's started!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?!\NThey're not here yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.18,0:17:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the song!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you crazy?! They'd get\Neven madder if we did that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.94,0:17:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm figuring that out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you have this song's lyrics?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.57,0:17:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Yeah,\Nthey're in that CD case...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.70,0:17:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, what do you want them for...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.12,0:17:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're not gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.55,0:18:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Break my lies ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Chase after me again as I rush off ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Save my heart ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.10,0:18:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ I'm actually waiting... Embrace me... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.06,0:18:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Now return to love ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could swear I've heard\Nthat singing voice before...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't joke like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell's singing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.20,0:18:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about tone-deaf...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it is Takayama-{\i1}san{\i0}'s voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.79,0:18:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.55,0:18:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ It hurt that I couldn't\Nsay that one little thing ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ as I sought this\Nwarm hand almost in tears ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.74,0:18:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.41,0:19:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Even so, I searched because\NI still believed deep down ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Break my lies ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.50,0:19:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Realize the quivering \Ntruth in my eyes ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.17,0:19:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Save my heart ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.21,0:19:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Kiss these trembling lips ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Now return to love ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ What I felt when I was\N with you wasn't weakness ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.95,0:19:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ it was a kind of serenity that\Nmade up for something I lacked ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ The more important the person,\Nthe more afraid I am to lose them ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.96,0:20:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ All alone in the crowd,\NI searched for a place to return to ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.35,0:20:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Break my lies ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.43,0:20:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Snatch away the pain-- ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.81,0:20:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so the Two-Mix concert that we\Nbarged into ended without a hitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Now return to love ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya later!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work today!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.83,0:20:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work today!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.54,0:20:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.00,0:20:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what did you think\Nof singing on stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the greatest!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.05,0:20:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.46,0:20:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet! Just once, and you're hooked!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what did the little detective think?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.85,0:20:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was the concert?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. It was ok, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.85,0:20:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cheeky!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.90,0:21:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.40,0:21:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, this is your dressing room?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.11,0:21:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Inspector! Can we help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.24,0:21:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to ask when\Nyou're so exhausted,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I was hoping you could come\Nto the station to give a statement...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.88,0:21:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay. Just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.96,0:21:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, take your time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.42,0:21:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a wonderful concert!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.89,0:21:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.47,0:21:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.27,0:21:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is for saving us today!\NPractice at home, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.14,0:21:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.52,0:21:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And some for you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.15,0:21:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could I get autographs\Nand pictures, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.91,0:21:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.78,0:21:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready?! What's 1 plus 1?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.26,0:23:34.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Karaoke Box
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.22,0:23:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Break my lies ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.27,0:23:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Chase after me\Nagain as I rush off ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.60,0:23:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all he's been singing...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.90,0:23:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he hasn't gotten any better...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.81,0:23:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ I'm actually waiting...\NEmbrace me... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.69,0:23:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Now return to love ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.41,0:23:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Return to love ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.36,0:24:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old man was staying at the\Nhospital, but just when he woke up,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.79,0:24:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he witnessed a murder in the opposite\Nward and rushed to the scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.33,0:24:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.51,0:24:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man! Dr. Eto!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.37,0:24:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Eto's murderer was you, Mori-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.89,0:24:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.22,0:24:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! The old man fell into a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.24,0:24:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Conan...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.56,0:24:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The General Hospital Murder Case."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.30,0:24:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.82,0:24:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.84,0:24:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode takes place at a scary hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.86,0:24:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like needles!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.13,0:24:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
